{"tid":1545478,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登區選協調計劃","createTime":"2019-09-06T02:27:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T03:24:13.000Z","uid":22624,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b04fe9716c78d4db05dfdde66b6ed44a8d370f06","tid":1545478,"uid":22624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:27:45.000Z","msg":"今次大學選區出現任嘉兒被迫走，睇到好撚嬲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一直以嚟泛民選舉協調都搞唔起，因為裡面太多山頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，大黨又壟斷資料，仲未計扮黃實紅呢啲仆街，結果內鬥完都協調唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有見於此，不如就由連登呢個獨立平台幫泛民本土做協調啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n方法好簡單：<br />\n<br />\n1. 提名<br />\n由連登仔喺每個選區提名候選人（包括已經宣佈參選，如果當區冇同路人，就由連登仔提）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 初選<br />\n決定好候選人後，由連登仔喺連登用正負皮直接投票，就算你唔喺嗰區都可以照投，因為今次係全香港人嘅選戰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 投票<br />\n到投票時，大家只要根據初選結果投票即可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個只係好初步諗法，希望拋磚引玉，歡迎大家完善個計劃，希望可以善用今次冇大台嘅經驗，幫到區選同之後嘅立法會選舉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b2a94733de87a461b80fe23cffd4e7f162fe418","tid":1545478,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:27:57.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a07ba7579bfacc5467a20fb0a477e8cb61a590f3","tid":1545478,"uid":285194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:29:41.000Z","msg":"冇咁多市民睇連登<br />\n隨時好似雷動咁炒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"235a1e520fb96c641c3fdb21458e6cac57029d16","tid":1545478,"uid":244546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:34:03.000Z","msg":"真心好重要!!! 推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為我懶 借個位黎<br />\n各位選民注意呀!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545405\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545405</a>"},{"pid":"7e4fb012460bc67698d4326a1c33d15e53276378","tid":1545478,"uid":197121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:38:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"85ca272efc371d7c615a612c06012ce2737c5e4f","tid":1545478,"uid":244546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:39:16.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6add61224ca5d7b23a3d824f8a5daafd01dd5a0d","tid":1545478,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:40:00.000Z","msg":"已經太遲<br />\n總之收咗譚香文皮先<br />\n然後確定每區邊個可信就幫佢啦"},{"pid":"1d6d5a966ae45e9accede46a37b4b4d33e11b0b6","tid":1545478,"uid":22624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:52:49.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"f5238d92606bec33316793296fdfc44bf9115a95","tid":1545478,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:08:55.000Z","msg":"此回